Module com.boslott

Package com.boslott.DataAccess

  • Interface Summary
    Interface Description
    AppointmentDAO
    An AppointmentDAO is a Data Access Object with the methods needed to interact with Appointment data
    ContactDAO
    A ContactDAO is a Data Access Object with the methods needed to interact with Contact data
    CountryDAO
    A CountryDAO is a Data Access Object with the methods needed to interact with Country data
    CustomerDAO
    A CustomerDAO is a Data Access Object with all the methods needed to interact with Customer data
    DivisionDAO
    A DivsionDAO is a Data Access Object with the needed methods to interact with First-Level Division data
    UserDAO
    A UserDAO is a Data Access Object with the needed methods to interact with User data
  • Class Summary
    Class Description
    UCertdbAppointmentDAO
    A UCertdbAppointmentDAO object is an Appointment Data Access Object used to interact with Appointment data from a UCertify database
    UCertdbContactDAO
    A UCertdbContactDAO object is a Contact Data Access Object used to interact with Contact data from a UCertify database
    UCertdbCountryDAO
    A UCertdbCountryDAO object is a Country Data Access Object used to interact with Country data from a UCertify database data source
    UCertdbCustomerDAO
    A UCertdbCustomerDAO object is a CustomerDAO object used to interact with Customer data from a UCertify database data source
    UCertdbDAOFactory
    A UCertdbDAOFactory object is a factory object used to create UCertdbDAO objects.
    UCertdbDivisionDAO
    An UCertdbDivisionDAO object is a DivisionDAO object used to interact with Division data from the UCertify database data source
    UCertdbUserDAO
    A UCertdbUserDAO object is a UserDAO object used to interact with User data from the UCertify database data source
